I have a living will with my request for certain procedures not to be used (no machines to keep me alive unless I'm pregnant sorta thing) but I wish I could make a living will that would state my wish to die if I were ever in that sort of position, or was wasting away with alsiemers or any number of other illnesses where I don't consider it to be life.<br>
