my family.  Some could not handle it and distanced themselves, others fell apart and just gibbered uselessly, the couple of us that were left got screwed into taking care of everything.  Giving her injections, wiping her soiled and chemo corrupted body, feeding her semi-consious and deleroius.<br>
<br>
Yeah, I have issues.  Euthanasia is one. <p><br>
